      <h1 style="font-size:2.2rem;font-weight:800;margin-bottom:0.5rem;">PTCL Bill Online — Landline & Broadband</h1>
      <p style="opacity:0.9;font-size:1.1rem;margin-bottom:2rem;">Check your PTCL bill for landline, DSL, FlashFiber, CharJi, or EVO. Enter your phone number or Account ID.</p>
      <div style="background:white;border-radius:16px;padding:2rem;max-width:580px;color:#1a1a1a;">
