        <p style="font-size:0.85rem;color:#555;margin-bottom:1rem;">Use your PTCL phone number OR 10-digit Account ID. Both work.</p>
        <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:0.5rem;margin-bottom:0.8rem;">
          <input id="ptcl-phone" type="text" placeholder="Phone number without area code (e.g. 5712345)"
            style="padding:0.75rem 1rem;border:2px solid #e2e8f0;border-radius:8px;font-size:1rem;" />
